  m_Name: BarnabasNode1
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  options:
  - optionText: "I\u2019m looking for something called the Farm Restorer. Have you
      heard of it?"
    replyText: "I\u2019ve heard of the Farm Restorer. I can help you, but first,
      do something for us. To the east, there\u2019s an old gas station. Find 3 supply
      packages there and bring them to the village, then we\u2019ll talk."
    nextNode: 1
    exitOption: 0
    conditionType: 0
    questID: 0
    objectID: 0
    amountObject: 0
    actions:
    - {fileID: 11400000, guid: f0b3edb9fc2d3374cac2381c5083886a, type: 2}
  - optionText: What happened to your eye?
    replyText: "That\u2019s a long story\u2026 Before Clearwater even existed, I
      was traveling with a caravan. One night, bandits from Texas attacked us - I
      was the only one who made it out alive. I killed them all with my shotgun\u2026
      but one of their bullets damaged my eye."
    nextNode: 0
    exitOption: 0
    conditionType: 0
    questID: 0
    objectID: 0
    amountObject: 0
    actions: []
  - optionText: "Do you have a wife\u2026 or is it just you and your son, Colby?"
    replyText: "I don\u2019t have a wife. Not anymore. She died giving birth\u2026
      Back then, there wasn\u2019t even a doctor in the village. It\u2019s just been
      me and the boy since. I\u2019m doing what I can to raise him right."
    nextNode: 0
    exitOption: 0
    conditionType: 0
    questID: 0
    objectID: 0
    amountObject: 0
    actions: []
  - optionText: Nothing. Thank you, I have to go now.
    replyText: 
    nextNode: 0
    exitOption: 1
    conditionType: 0
    questID: 0
    objectID: 0
    amountObject: 0
    actions: []
